content.rendered:
Directed by Arvindr Khaira

Written by Janni

Cast Akshay Kumar. Ammy Virk. Nupur Sanon. Praak (B Praak)

Languages Hindi

Producers Azeem Dayani. Ashish Dixit. Aadesh Gola. Vikrant Kaushik. Aron Paharia. Art Direction by. Akhilesh Suhas. Makeup Department. Pradeep Kumar. Visual Effects by. Shudhanshu Jaiswal

Production Cape of Good Film
